title: Corey Corpodian - Unleash Success With Emotional Fitness
itunes:title: Corey Corpodian - Unleash Success With Emotional Fitness
description:
When is it best to act on your emotions and channel them in ways to push you forward in your business? When is it best to hold them back and make conscious decisions?
 
And what is emotional fitness?
 
Corey Corpodian is the host of Unleash success and author of Emotional Fitness.
 
In this interview, we get to the bottom of these questions and map out how to get emotionally fit to generate massive success in your life.
 
Show Notes: https://underdogempowerment.com/corey-corpodian/
